{"word":"G4379 - προσψαύω - prospsaúō - pros-psow'-o - Touch","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσψαύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prospsaúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-psow'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Touch</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தொடு"},{"paragraph":"to touch"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and <b>&#x03C8;&#x03B1;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>psauo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>touch</i>); to <i>impinge</i>, that is, <i>lay a finger on</i> (in order to relieve): - touch.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}